posts.post_title: 1893 N135 Honest Long Cut - Talk of Diamond - SGC 30
posts.post_content:
1893 N135 Honest Long Cut - Left on Base - Talk of the Diamond in an SGC 30.  Excellent graphics on this card.  Pictured on the left is the drawing of a baseball player, and on the right is a comic drawing.  One of the more desirable sets that you just don't see cards from very often.

$60 now takes it!

Ok... i just want to move this card... the first $60 takes it... delivered!
This has been sold thank you!
